  "description": "PLAY DEAD 0.85 + BELLY 0.6 — the possum playing dead in a warm space. Slow filter sweep over long attack, body still, sub oscillator persisting below the threshold of threat. This is not absence — it is suspension. The animal is alive inside its stillness. Room reverb keeps the warmth from evaporating. TRASH and BITE both zero: no teeth, no noise, only held breath.",
